<div class="comment-content">
<p>I know One Piece, but don&#8217;t know anything about D&amp;D tabletop games. I know people that love sci-fi like Star Wars but can&#8217;t stand fantasy so they won&#8217;t watch the Lord of the Rings. Different people have different interests even in similar genres. No everyone geeks out the same.</p>
</div> 
