<li class="comment byuser comment-author-kidvi even depth-2" id="li-comment-512930">
<article id="comment-512930" class="comment-body">
<footer class="comment-meta">
<div class="comment-author vcard"><img src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/091310f5af7485b0c28b050f481fa3ab?s=50&#038;d=mm&#038;r=pg" width="50" height="50" alt="" class="avatar avatar-50wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-50 alignnone photo avatar-default"/><span class="fn"><b>kidvi</b> <br/><a href="http://www.wuxiaworld.com/ti-index/ti-vol-12-chapter-8-1/#comment-512930"><time datetime="2016-11-30T16:20:26+00:00"> November 30, 2016 at 4:20 pm</time></a></span></div> </footer> 
<div class="comment-content">
<p>The mines can only be triggered by weight.</p>
<p>So the safest way is to have the dragon step on it, otherwise they may get hurt as well.</p>
</div> 
